      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Ian Osgood</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.quora.com/profile/Ian-Osgood-1\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/a/a8/IanOsgood.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:IanOsgood.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ian Osgood <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Ian Osgood</b>,<br />\nan American software developer <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, chess player, chess coach and tournament director <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nHe is author of <a href=\"/FCP\" title=\"FCP\">FCP</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \nthe <a href=\"/Forth\" title=\"Forth\">Forth</a> Chess Program, originally derived from <a href=\"/Tom_Kerrigan\" title=\"Tom Kerrigan\">Tom Kerrigan's</a> simple chess program <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a>, and the Forth <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> playing program <i>FGP</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ian_Osgood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ian_Osgood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=24629\">Re: [Q</a> What is Genius' speed?] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 13, 1998 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=26173\">Looking for Novag Sapphire/Diamond/UCB serial port pinout</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 08, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Novag_Sapphire\" title=\"Novag Sapphire\">Novag Sapphire</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ian_Osgood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=213382\">Re: Question for Ian Osgood (NT)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Deep_Green&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Deep Green (page does not exist)\">Deep Green</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=252881\">TSCP enhancements (Re: Short chess programs)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 19, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=17627\">A bit of history from the CCC Archives</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 06, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=20688\">History: US Open Computer Championship crosstables?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 16, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/United_States_Open_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"United States Open Computer Chess Championship\">United States Open Computer Chess Championship</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=25892\">CCT replaces ICGA's event for the World Championship?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=29692&amp;start=9\">Re: Go FORTH and multiply with FCP...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 08, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ian_Osgood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=33093\">What happened to schachcomputer.info?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37938\">MacHack under PDP-10 emulation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Mac_Hack\" title=\"Mac Hack\">Mac Hack</a>, <a href=\"/PDP-10\" title=\"PDP-10\">PDP-10</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=42564\">Rating list history</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 22, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Rating_Lists\" title=\"Engine Rating Lists\">Engine Rating Lists</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=49858\">Fritz Leiber's \"The 64-Square Madhouse\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 28, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/The_Bernstein_Chess_Program\" title=\"The Bernstein Chess Program\">The Bernstein Chess Program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=58176\">UCI OwnBook shim?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=49533&amp;start=30\">Re: Ferret 1.00 v258 - program from 1995</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ian Osgood</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Ferret\" title=\"Ferret\">Ferret</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ian_Osgood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wiki.c2.com/?IanOsgood\">Ian Osgood - C2 Wiki</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wiki.c2.com/?GameOfChess\">Game Of Chess - C2 Wiki</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.quirkster.com/iano/forth/FCP.html\">Ian Osgood's Forth Chess Program (FCP)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.quirkster.com/iano/forth/fgp.html\">Ian Osgood's Forth Go Program (FGP)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessgames.com/perl/chessplayer?pid=157604\">The chess games of Ian Osgood</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.quora.com/profile/Ian-Osgood-1\">an Osgood - Quora</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ian_Osgood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: